5. Comparison to Existing Reports

While this report discusses the efficacy of antipsychotic medications with birth

control, it is essential to note that previous reports have focused on the

potential risks associated with these combinations. This report aims to provide

a more balanced view by exploring both the benefits and drawbacks of using

antipsychotics in conjunction with hormonal contraceptives.
